name: Tiny Device #02: Mint-o-Meter
description: This #OBJKT shows minted NFTs per hour on hicetnunc, local min & max values with a timeline showing the current local date & time. You can explore the data by: 1) Rotating the knob, 2) Mouse wheel, 3) Panning the graph directly, 4) Keyboard Left & Right arrows. Many thanks to better-call.dev. Made by https://twitter.com/neelts.
